{"tid":1726391,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（冇分化撚 ok？）喺連登分析形勢，如落場幫手協調一吓","createTime":"2019-11-16T06:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T09:55:33.000Z","uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46f58e44fc5cb86cb8cd9629b09e973a2da1182b","tid":1726391,"uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:42:54.000Z","msg":"見到有啲連登手足都講棄橋，讓路係幾on9<br />\n又話暴大係象徵，應該要留<br />\n<br />\n另一邊又話be water，保住前線<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">拗嚟拗去，大家只係集中揾不同點，忘記咗大家都係同路人</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大家都只係愛之深，責之切</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前線其實都有不停討論去定留，但始終年輕<br />\n小組討論方邊未能拎到5**<br />\n<br />\n&quot;留定撤？大家舉手決定，呀！都係企兩邊&quot;<br />\n留守手足其實都講咗set完rb，popo一攻就會走。覺得popo嚟都唔走，反而popo唔嚟就走？<br />\n走嘅手足又以為要全力抵抗，加上無人嚟support都好心up又好攰<br />\n<br />\n見到冇人協調，圍埋成日都係表決留定走<br />\n又冇傾過留嘅之後會點<br />\n又有一，兩個出位啲，有陣dominate，同spin咗第個point<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>如果有人梳理吓，唔駛落judgement嘅，就會smooth好多</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n前線手足其實真係唔得閒睇連登，瞓得兩，三個鐘<br />\n都難免暴躁，做哨都會係咁屌人影相<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">大家真係有時間嘅，係未有危險前，走去前線同手足傾吓偈啦，提醒大家be humble，做好作戰準備</span><br />\n見前線玩車玩膠玩魔法，check嘢過火嘅話，咪提一提水，大家自己友，前線唔夠瞓係咁架啦<br />\n<br />\n論壇都係咁屌鬼嘅話<br />\n前線嗰種等咗兩日都冇事發生，見到不停有人走既心態<br />\n係幾咁不安呀！打緊仗呀！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">做咗咩決定好，都可以幫手comfort另一邊前線感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n正如呢度連登一樣，手足唔同立場都respect吓，唔好下下話人吹風撚，打殘自己士氣。見到堅負面嘅吹風post，咪拉! 真係唔gur，咪到現場真係感受吓，比前線一個support<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>真係分化撚永遠都係唔夠我哋人多，運用我哋影響力蓋過佢哋，互相尊重，集思廣益，現場做到達至共識或妥協，去到呢一步，大家已經好叻架喇</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：模擬緊現場小組討論情況，預備dse oral考試"},{"pid":"d34fecf327cb916b5aab76e6326044146c1d79ea","tid":1726391,"uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:43:20.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"c70f226800c4d03d6745a5e3da706272cbed7655","tid":1726391,"uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:44:51.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"d766cddc432356d0230fd915c0b8420b32f2c063","tid":1726391,"uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:45:47.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"41837c6870ea76127c8ec321cfe7c06643ebe347","tid":1726391,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:50:08.000Z","msg":"係咪剩係得我一個on99,每朝等開花<br />\n<br />\n［中場檢討］係黎明行動，唔係黃昏行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1725989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1725989</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a7637c24e1896d609179d6ae15f553feaee12b83","tid":1726391,"uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"f6dfbdaa978932376c774788e228869d2eb44bc5","tid":1726391,"uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:06:13.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"5cd2646881c57b342ce1dddf32ac282e725196ee","tid":1726391,"uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:08:45.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"f66cbf1fe9dec5e1900b30c08961eb9a4673463f","tid":1726391,"uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:19:30.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"e2725f1851b32c992213e50ba9d9cd9d065d0c25","tid":1726391,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:20:17.000Z","msg":"［區選］藍絲散水運動，正式開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726325</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cd3330d54cdc11d5f735d566b7bdb0f12bfd556a","tid":1726391,"uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:10:14.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"71a389de1f5406d3a529fca69393b3c241cba1f8","tid":1726391,"uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"1dfa781f870e46af5a26b3f422dafe3714031918","tid":1726391,"uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"fb8a029ae40102b32d6729a65fc5f70a56359d4a","tid":1726391,"uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:55:18.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"f034c678864d15f9a98177c42c334437209a856a","tid":1726391,"uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:55:33.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"}]}